87
00:13:25,283 --> 00:13:28,284
Pergilah!
Aku akan melindungimu!

88
00:14:51,103 --> 00:14:52,402
Lantai terakhir.

89
00:14:52,404 --> 00:14:53,804
Senjatanya pasti berada
di sini.

90
