Jangan tembak aku.

101
00:15:32,878 --> 00:15:34,978
Kumohon jangan.

102
00:15:36,447 --> 00:15:37,881
Kau mengompol.

103
00:15:37,883 --> 00:15:39,316
Aku bukan anggota mereka.

104
00:15:39,318 --> 00:15:42,052
Namaku Dean.

105
00:15:42,054 --> 00:15:43,420
Kenapa kau masih bicara?

106
00:15:43,422 --> 00:15:46,456
Tara, tunggu.

107
00:15:46,458 --> 00:15:50,193
- Tunggu saja.
- Untuk apa?

108
00:15:50,195 --> 00:15:51,862
Dia angkat tangan, Tara.

109
00:15:51,864 --> 00:15:54,164
Kita punya tugas untuk
dilakukan.

110
00:15:56,869 --> 00:15:59,135
Kau mau memeriksa itu?

111
00:16:10,883 --> 00:16:12,349
Kita kehilangan orang dari
tim lain.

112
00:16:12,351 --> 00:16:14,084
Morgan?

113
00:16:14,284 --> 00:16:15,520
Aku tidak tahu.

114
00:16:16,188 --> 00:16:17,954
Keluar.

115
00:16:25,699 --> 00:16:27,327
Tetaplah di situ.

116
00:16:27,666 --> 00:16:29,165
Kita saling menghalangi.

117
00:16:29,167 --> 00:16:30,367
Kami akan beri tanda
bila sudah aman.

118
00:16:30,369 --> 00:16:32,369
Bersiaplah.

119
